### 1. 회원가입 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser1@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!",
  "nickname": "테스트유저1",
  "phone": "01012345678"
}

### 2. 로그인 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/sign-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "testuser1@example.com",
  "password": "Test1234!"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("refreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### 3. 토큰 재발급 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/reissue
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{accessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{refreshToken}}"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("reissuedAccessToken", response.body.data.accessToken);
  client.global.set("reissuedRefreshToken", response.body.data.refreshToken);
%}

### 4. 로그아웃 성공
POST http://localhost:10000/api/v1/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: {{reissuedAccessToken}}

{
  "refreshToken": "{{reissuedRefreshToken}}"
}